# 🛒 Ecommerce Sales Dashboard – Power BI Project

## 📌 Overview
This Power BI dashboard analyzes a year’s worth of ecommerce sales data to provide actionable insights into sales performance, profit trends, product category performance, and customer payment preferences across different Indian states.

---

## 📊 Key Insights
- 💰 **Total Profit**: 37K  
- 💳 **Top Payment Mode**: Cash on Delivery (44%)  
- 🛍️ **Top Selling Category**: Clothing (63% of total quantity)  
- 📈 **Best Performing Month**: December (10.3K profit)  
- 🔻 **Lowest Performing Month**: May (-3.7K loss)

---

## 📂 Dashboard Features
- 💡 **Monthly Profit Trend** bar chart
- 🌐 **State-wise Filter** for regional performance
- 📦 **Quantity Breakdown** by Product Category and Payment Mode (Donut Charts)
- 🔍 **Sub-Category Profit Analysis** (Bar Chart)
- 📅 **Quarter Selector** for seasonal insights

---

## 📁 Dataset Description
- **Type**: Ecommerce sales transactional data
- **Time Period**: 1 year
- **Columns Used**: State, Category, Sub-Category, Quantity, Profit, Payment Mode, Month

---

## 🛠 Tools Used
- **Power BI Desktop**
- Power Query for data cleaning and transformation
- DAX for calculated measures and KPIs
- Slicers for interactivity and drill-down analysis

---

## 📥 How to Use
1. Download the `.pbix` file from this repository.
2. Open it using [Power BI Desktop](https://powerbi.microsoft.com/desktop/).
3. Use filters and slicers to explore the data interactively.

---

## 🔐 Notes
- Data is fictional or sample-based and used for educational purposes.
- All visuals are interactive and can be filtered by state, quarter, and more.

